{
  "stem": "7600.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I did learn-- in the year and a half or two years that I was there, I learned French because you had a lot of homework.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was no fudging or-- you had to do your work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- and the most important thing was all of our-- all of our teachers were men, and they were all professors-- PhDs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they would-- they wouldn't take any, you know, fuss or anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You couldn't-- you had to do your work, and that was it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I did fairly well, except in-- in math.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't so good in math.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I got a tutor for math.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I did well in French.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I did well in German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "German is a difficult language.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know whether you know, but the-- the grammar in German alone can kill you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You learn this all your life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, right?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Isn't it?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When people tell me here today-- when I came here, said, oh, English is the hardest language, I said, English is [? not a ?] language.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To me, that was nothing to learn English.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was the easiest language I've ever heard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Had to know grammar.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The only thing difficult in the English language is the spelling.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But German and French grammar is very difficult.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as I said, I did a lot of other things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I learned to swim when I was five, and I was a very good swimmer-- the breaststroke.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I never learned to crawl because I didn't-- the-- apparently, the-- the chlorine in the water bothered my sinuses, so I gave it up.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I couldn't-- I-- they tried to teach me how to dive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that also bothered me, so the teacher said forget about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Just swim.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I got sick from it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
